@page "/studio"

<PageTitle>RVR Studio</PageTitle>

<h1>RVR Studio</h1>
<p class="studio-subtitle">Creez, gerez et publiez vos projets RIVORA Framework.</p>

<div class="studio-grid">
    <a href="/studio/new" class="studio-card studio-card-primary">
        <div class="studio-card-icon">+</div>
        <h3>Nouvelle Solution</h3>
        <p>Wizard interactif pour creer une solution RIVORA personnalisee de A a Z.</p>
        <span class="studio-card-action">Commencer</span>
    </a>

    <a href="/studio/modules" class="studio-card">
        <div class="studio-card-icon">M</div>
        <h3>Gestionnaire de Modules</h3>
        <p>Ajouter ou retirer des modules RIVORA dans un projet existant.</p>
        <span class="studio-card-action">Gerer</span>
    </a>

    <a href="/health" class="studio-card">
        <div class="studio-card-icon">H</div>
        <h3>Health Dashboard</h3>
        <p>Surveillez l'etat de sante de vos services et dependances.</p>
        <span class="studio-card-action">Voir</span>
    </a>

    <a href="/audit" class="studio-card">
        <div class="studio-card-icon">A</div>
        <h3>Audit Logs</h3>
        <p>Consultez les logs d'audit et tracez les actions utilisateur.</p>
        <span class="studio-card-action">Consulter</span>
    </a>
</div>

<h2 style="margin-top: 2.5rem;">Actions rapides</h2>

<div class="studio-actions">
    <div class="studio-action-card">
        <h4>CLI</h4>
        <p>Installez le CLI pour generer depuis le terminal :</p>
        <code>dotnet tool install --global RVR.CLI</code>
    </div>

    <div class="studio-action-card">
        <h4>Documentation</h4>
        <p>Consultez la documentation complete :</p>
        <a href="https://khalilbenaz.github.io/RIVORA/" target="_blank">khalilbenaz.github.io/RIVORA</a>
    </div>

    <div class="studio-action-card">
        <h4>Telecharger Desktop</h4>
        <p>Application native Windows / macOS / Linux :</p>
        <a href="https://github.com/khalilbenaz/RIVORA/releases/latest" target="_blank">Derniere release</a>
    </div>
</div>
